      • create

        public static javafx.scene.control.Tab create​()
        Method that creates the Detail tab and sets up the initial charts. Includes default start station and year: Aberporth and 2017, respectively.
        Returns:
        Tab, detailTab

      • updateWeatherData

        private static void updateWeatherData​(java.lang.String station,
                                      int year)
        Method that updates that private WeatherDataCollection, weatherCollection with data for the chosen station and year. Station data is collected from the loaded WeatherDataMap allStations in the SummaryTab. This data is filtered by year using the getWeatherDataYear method from WeatherDataCollection and saved in the weather ArrayList.
        Parameters:
        station - , the weather station to view data for
        year - , the year to view data for
        See Also:
        WeatherDataCollection, WeatherDataMap

      • updateComparisonTempChart

        private static void updateComparisonTempChart​(java.lang.String station,
                                              int year)
        Method that updates the temperatureComparison line-chart. Any current data series in the chart will be deleted before new series are added for each WeatherData instance in the current WeatherData arrayList for that year.
        Parameters:
        station - , the weather station to view data for
        year - , the year to view data for
        See Also:
        WeatherData
